HEADWORD: Propane
<hw>Pro"pane</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Propy</ets>l +
meth<ets>ane</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A heavy gaseous
hydrocarbon, <chform>C3H8</chform>, of the paraffin series, occurring
naturally dissolved in crude petroleum, and also made artificially; --
called also <altname>propyl hydride</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

